sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Typography, Container, Grid, Card, CardContent, List, ListItem, ListItemIcon, ListItemText, Paper, IconButton, } from '@mui/material'; import { Check as CheckIcon, Star as StarIcon, Group as GroupIcon, People as PeopleIcon, School as SchoolIcon, HowToReg as HowToRegIcon, EmojiObjects as EmojiObjectsIcon, ArrowDownward as ArrowDownwardIcon, } from '@mui/icons-material'; const Two = () => { return ( Teacher Perceptions Unlocking Insights Through Experience Interview Analysis and Qualitative Results The interview with the 18-year veteran educator with an immigrant background yielded qualitative results and analysis that align with the principles of lifelong learning and educational reform as outlined in "Education: The Necessary Utopia" from The Treasure Within: Report to UNESCO of the International Commission on Education for the Twenty-first Century. The key themes and findings from the interview resonate with the principles of ongoing learning and the transformative vision for education discussed in the UNESCO report, emphasizing the relevance and applicability of these principles in the context of the teacher's experiences and perspectives. {/* Themes Addressed */} Themes Addressed {/* List Item Example */} {/* Add more list items as needed */} {/* Qualitative Results and Analysis */} Qualitative Results and Analysis {/* List Item Example */} {/* Add more list items as needed */} {/* Recommendation Alignment */} Recommendation Alignment {/* List Item Example */} {/* Add more list items as needed */} {/* Container for Form Response Screenshots */} {/* You can add images here */} {/* Example: */} {/* Add more Grid items for additional screenshots */} ); }; export default Two;
